{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/construction","result":{"data":{"prismicProject":{"uid":"construction","id":"aed9bcba-1d7a-5298-8c9c-9663d050c66d","data":{"project_title":{"html":"<h1>CONSTRUCTION</h1>","text":"CONSTRUCTION"},"project_page_color":"White","project_intro":{"html":"<p>Poster and promotional materials for London based photography exhibition, Construction. The project supported the work of emerging and established artists whilst raising awareness for Protection Approaches - a charity working to defend the rights of people around the world who are violently targeted because of their identity. Artist donated work was then auctioned to raise funds for the organisation. <br /><br />The lead images highlight the work of Marguerite Bornhauser and Suzie Howell and the custom typography was inspired by the movement and narratives captured in their work. The headlines were animated to follow movement patterns found in Suzie Howell&#39;s video work and then exported from different stages of the animation to create the subtly distorted titles.</p>","text":"Poster and promotional materials for London based photography exhibition, Construction. The project supported the work of emerging and established artists whilst raising awareness for Protection Approaches - a charity working to defend the rights of people around the world who are violently targeted because of their identity. Artist donated work was then auctioned to raise funds for the organisation. \n\nThe lead images highlight the work of Marguerite Bornhauser and Suzie Howell and the custom typography was inspired by the movement and narratives captured in their work. The headlines were animated to follow movement patterns found in Suzie Howell's video work and then exported from different stages of the animation to create the subtly distorted titles."},"categories":[{"category":{"document":{"__typename":"PrismicCategory","id":"10b78e8a-bbc2-51e8-9d1d-4ddaef3b40b2","data"